window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The quest for the World Stones concludes here!</p> <p>Charles must beat the Wraith Queen to at least one of the three Stones, or she'll open a portal and summon an unending horde, enough wraiths to suck all life from the world.</p> <p>At all costs-no matter how great the loss might be-at least one of the Stones must be obtained, or all is lost!</p> <p>But getting a Stone is just the beginning. World Stones are virtually indestructible, so even if they win one, how do they keep it from the Queen forever?</p> <p>To save the world, Charles will have to combine logic with magic if he's to end the threat of the Wraith Queen for all time!</p>"; 
